Beach + Convertible S Class Benz + @goldenbarbie = Video 

Fun Fact : This video came about from just chilling at Taj crib wit some friends & in between J’s & a few drinks we decided to wake up the next morning & shoot something. And what better video to shoot other then the song wit the title that got us to thinking.. Mad random but a vibe (in my most NYC accent 😂)
